<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ،<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١٧٠٩١ - عَنِ ابْنِ جُرَيْجٍ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> قُلْتُ لِعَطَاءٍ أَتَمْتَشِطُ الْمَرْأَةُ بِالسُّكْرِ قَالَ: <span class="c2">«لَا»</span>،<span class="c5"> وَقَالَ عَبْدُ الْكَرِيمِ:</span> <span class="c2">«لَا»</span> وَقَالَ عَمْرُو بْنُ دِينَارٍ: <span class="c2">«لَا تَمْتَشِطُ الْمَرْأَةُ بِالْخَمْرِ»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>